# ✅ Interview‑Friendly One‑Liner 💯

> The browser downloads the JavaScript bundle when it encounters `<script>` tags in the HTML, fetches them via HTTP, and executes them after HTML parsing—hydrating the server‑rendered markup to enable interactivity.

